10:T4dd,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Movie","name":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife","description":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/euDNoIcpeW69gJBUYktR0hewq47.jpg","datePublished":"2015-12-18","numberOfEpisodes":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["pink film","Mystery","Romance","Drama",null],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":4,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":3}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"7d1b2ed8-26ef-4ea9-94ab-b1ee74c4fb30","tmdb_id":693979,"imdb_id":"tt5306218","content_type":"movie","title":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife","original_title":"悦楽交差点 オンナの裏に出会うとき","overview":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]","poster_path":"/euDNoIcpeW69gJBUYktR0hewq47.jpg","backdrop_path":"/zOkRtPxtQ6Qi1jRFx7jQ0rSxYrw.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-18","first_air_date":null,"status":"published","original_language":"ja","origin_country":["JP"],"genres":[{"name":"pink film"},{"id":9648,"name":"Mystery"},{"id":10749,"name":"Romance"},{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},"pink film"],"popularity":3.5395,"vote_average":4,"vote_count":3,"runtime":71,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":null,"created_at":"2026-01-26T16:54:14.416776+00:00","updated_at":"2026-03-29T20:59:02.328+00:00","tagline":"","homepage":"https://okurapictures.com/all-films/the-secret-game-of-the-immoral-wife.html","budget":0,"revenue":0,"production_companies":[{"id":138285,"name":"Okura Pictures","logo_path":"/fjxX3f0XFIZYwUlpJkd4IAuNrWJ.png","origin_country":"JP"},{"id":263976,"name":"Production Lenny","logo_path":null,"origin_country":"JP"}],"production_countries":[{"name":"Japan","iso_3166_1":"JP"}],"spoken_languages":[{"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","english_name":"Japanese"}],"networks":[],"last_air_date":null,"in_production":null,"tmdb_status":"Released","content_rating":null,"keywords":[{"id":155477,"name":"softcore"},{"id":159551,"name":"pink film"},{"id":230960,"name":"unfaithful wife"}],"alternative_titles":[{"type":"original title, R18 version","title":"Etsuraku kôsaten: Onna no ura ni deau toki","iso_3166_1":"JP"},{"type":"R15 version","title":"悦楽交差点","iso_3166_1":"JP"}],"videos":[{"id":"683b149a1db03c402c7f389b","key":"4dR9xASZi24","name":"映画 『悦楽交差点』 予告編","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Trailer","official":false,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2016-08-04T09:16:38.000Z"}],"watch_providers":{"results":{}},"wikidata_id":null,"tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-07T14:49:53.785279+00:00","region":"JP","main_poster":"/sNKpMnsXNfW1778qOw0r7ZT4VMg.jpg","images":{"logos":[],"posters":[{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/sNKpMnsXNfW1778qOw0r7ZT4VMg.jpg","iso_639_1":"ja","vote_average":3.334},{"width":892,"height":1200,"file_path":"/d2vKr4fxrM8MnLgKCuvakmo3MwC.jpg","iso_639_1":"ja","vote_average":0.166},{"width":528,"height":750,"file_path":"/joPBBSgDvuV9hzJ40ktfZlE02kI.jpg","iso_639_1":"ja","vote_average":0},{"width":1200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/euDNoIcpeW69gJBUYktR0hewq47.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1200,"height":1695,"file_path":"/ypqW6kTwwHJHND1kaisxebLIvwi.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1500,"height":844,"file_path":"/zOkRtPxtQ6Qi1jRFx7jQ0rSxYrw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/iZ3qkFp6XJQb9d2jF5vAfthFCky.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/hx0uJuOqcLEcNDDaJOePzOriNmz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:19:24.951+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife","runtime":71,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://okurapictures.com/all-films/the-secret-game-of-the-immoral-wife.html","overview":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]"},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"悦乐交叉点","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在繁华街进行通行量调查的自由职业者春生(麻木贵仁饰)用眼睛追赶来来往往的女性,机械地数着数的他喃喃自语道:第一千个是我的媳妇,第一千个是我的媳妇......就在这时,一个年轻女子从春生面前走过,手边的柜台打了一千个......五年后,破旧公寓的墙上贴着一张女人的照片,对着春生微笑,那是曾经在繁华街看到的女人川岛真琴(古川伊织饰)的偷拍照。春生从那天起就一直保持着悄悄的跟踪行为,现在她的行动记录笔记已经超过了10本。那天晚上也用双筒望远镜窥视着真琴和丈夫・干也(田中靖教饰)的性爱,春生想着......『她真正的伴侣是我。总有一天神会发现错误并改变命运的..........."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"「千人目の女をオレの嫁にする!」","homepage":"","overview":"フリーターの春夫は通行量調査のバイトをしていた。行きかう女性をみながら、千人目は俺の嫁にすると妄想する。そのとき、若い女が通り過ぎる…。それから5年、春夫はかつて見かけた川島真琴のストーキング行為を続け、夜の営みの回数まで知るようになる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"悦樂交叉點","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在繁華街進行通行量調查的自由職業者春生 (麻木貴仁飾) 用眼睛追趕來來往往的女性, 機械地數著數的他喃喃自語道:第一千個是我的媳婦, 第一千個是我的媳婦. . . . . . 就在這時, 一個年輕女子從春生面前走過, 手邊的櫃台打了一千個. . . . . . 五年後, 破舊公寓的牆上貼著一張女人的照片, 對著春生微笑, 那是曾經在繁華街看到的女人川島真琴 (古川伊織飾) 的偷拍照。春生從那天起就一直保持著悄悄的跟蹤行為, 現在她的行動記錄筆記已經超過了 10 本。那天晚上也用雙筒望遠鏡窺視著真琴和丈夫・幹也 (田中靖教飾) 的性愛, 春生想著. . . . . . 『她真正的伴侶是我。總有一天神會發現錯誤並改變命運的. . . . . . . . . . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":433620,"adult":false,"title":"Suck It Up","video":false,"overview":"Ronnie lost her brother. Faye lost her first love. These two best friends set off on a debaucherous road trip to the mountains to get over the death of the man they both loved.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4835,"vote_count":37,"poster_path":"/rXLK3mjOt3hJnjaLhE6HfBADRUg.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/1bRqrHvlzebuzKkxFLkl5483FrZ.jpg","original_title":"Suck It Up","original_language":"en"},{"id":48741,"adult":false,"title":"Fur of Flying","video":false,"overview":"Wile E. Coyote fashions himself a homemade helicopter helmet, utilizing an assortment of mail order products. Soaring through the sky and over the cliffs, it's a surefire way to catch the Road Runner... assuming he can avoid military testing grounds.","genre_ids":[16,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1428,"vote_count":29,"poster_path":"/fnBecUruOZTDaJyO5HvNY7CiH1t.jpg","release_date":"2010-09-24","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/5MrL4OXCh4VOgn9LaJSn3bdlTI8.jpg","original_title":"Fur of Flying","original_language":"en"},{"id":548814,"adult":false,"title":"The Future Is Ours","video":false,"overview":"After a rough night out protesting in the city, Kosta and Maja fall in the hands of the police. Their lives will change forever.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0717,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/jIw3AIwj2oOK2mmLRSkz7X4mmcp.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-27","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Иднината е наша","original_language":"mk"},{"id":102151,"adult":false,"title":"Battle of Blood Island","video":false,"overview":"Two American GIs are the only survivors of a unit wiped out in a battle with Japanese troops on an isolated island. The two, who don't like each other, find try to put aside their differences in order to evade the Japanese and survive.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2158,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/nyeWPAfywDswd4Yt77nj3ZtgQEw.jpg","release_date":"1960-04-08","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/igOYCxWTmSyLfxBb7D9XezKoQWV.jpg","original_title":"Battle of Blood Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":1175147,"adult":false,"title":"Anything for a Pop Star 2","video":false,"overview":"Three friends who live in Resende, in the interior of Rio de Janeiro, and plan a trip in Babette's Beetle convertible to celebrate their 15 years of friendship and attend the closing show of the tour of a great pop star, who studied with them as a teenager. and today he is the most famous young singer in Brazil.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3182,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/jgLQlvInbiHp58QUpdMVc0FBjcW.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-10","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/dexTU2FeD5PmJ3jbWskgq5aWAZP.jpg","original_title":"Tudo por um Pop Star 2","original_language":"pt"},{"id":308868,"adult":false,"title":"People","video":false,"overview":"PEOPLE is a new collaboration of riders and filmers from Mack Dawg Productions. Directed by Pierre Minhondo and Justin Eeles.  This newly formed collective combines the talents, attitude, and fun-loving folks from such films as kidsKNOW’s “Burning Bridges,” and Neoproto’s “Some Kinda Life”. Learn, watch, and follow these PEOPLE as they show you real snowboarding in their own form.  From our cities to yours, look forward to watching: Jon Kooley, Justin Hebbel, Nima Jalali, Jordan Mendenhall, Curtis Woodman, Mitch Nelson, Bryan Fox, Etienne Gilbert, Robbie Sell, Stephen Duke, Pat McCarthy, Shaun McKay, Josh Mills, Marius Otterstad, Jussi Tarvainen, and Ryan Thompson. -Released August 2006.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2874,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/hKbnazFHwUQnaTMIrszodh9esVU.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-07","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"People","original_language":"en"},{"id":245464,"adult":false,"title":"Hello","video":false,"overview":"The film tells the story of three best friends named Ako, Aki and Awang, who are well-known in their village for their mischievous and humourous pranks. The trio work for Pak Man. One day, they are assigned to pick up his daughter Misha, who has just returned from overseas and dreams of becoming a doctor. The trio have been in love with her for a long time but she does not pay them any heed. When Misha is robbed by a snatch thief one day, she is rescued by a doctor named Shafiq. Her face reminds the doctor of his late wife, and he begins to pursue her, which annoys the trio.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4654,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2013-10-17","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hello","original_language":"en"},{"id":549115,"adult":false,"title":"Lío de faldas","video":false,"overview":"Five artsy young women in a group house have landlord troubles.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.181,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/rKWsLxgz9ATzrRmfpVz0jqjoWAU.jpg","release_date":"1969-09-18","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Lío de faldas","original_language":"es"},{"id":519676,"adult":false,"title":"Kolobok","video":false,"overview":"A collection of cartoons, each of which is a uniquely decorated folk tale.","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1943,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/ci5lzeikEnf5rooEo2QiWta21Pf.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-04","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":"/qAWHQIbZMjjy8GfvvNxXrRL5uUS.jpg","original_title":"Колобок","original_language":"ru"},{"id":525586,"adult":false,"title":"Uzeyir's Life","video":false,"overview":"The historical film about Azerbaijan composer Uzeyir Hadjibeyov's life.","genre_ids":[10402,99,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9553,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/ckOhPATBS2W7cHXQf9BR7g1ut37.jpg","release_date":"1981-12-20","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/vboCvyPMtT3C5UZIQbRyF8it1cA.jpg","original_title":"Üzeyir Ömrü","original_language":"az"},{"id":1186987,"adult":false,"title":"The Tower of Pisa","video":false,"overview":"Story of a typical Romanian couple in crisis.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3213,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/nO3jJexEzPB1FUGYR7LqEqotf2x.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-01","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Turnul din Pisa","original_language":"ro"},{"id":211995,"adult":false,"title":"Creep","video":false,"overview":"Angus Lynch, a psycho, escapes from prison and hooks up with his stripper sister named Kascha. Some death ensues eventually leading Angus to cross paths with a police captain named David who has a daughter named Jackie and whose wife was murdered when she was a child.","genre_ids":[9648,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1509,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/kRAleft62R02xtwxrJ1ysfx35V1.jpg","release_date":"1995-01-01","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Creep","original_language":"en"},{"id":479608,"adult":false,"title":"Mon amour, mon ami","video":false,"overview":"Daniela and Fouad live in Gubbio, and they both come from the sea: she is from Bari, he is from Casablanca. Their bodies have suffered hardships and alcoholism. They met by chance and a deep and healing friendship was born, which led them to live together. Now that Fouad needs a permit to stay, marriage seems to be the easiest solution. Daniela agrees to it, but as the wedding approaches, the ambiguity of Fouad’s feelings begins to worry her. Can you fake- marry someone who really loves you?","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1015,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/4l20ACKI3PN48AKbq1tkmH6K4f.jpg","release_date":"2017-08-31","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Mon amour, mon ami","original_language":"en"},{"id":717320,"adult":false,"title":"Tutankhamun In Colour","video":false,"overview":"The BBC version of \"King Tut In Color\" documentary. A century after the world’s most exciting archaeological find - the tomb of Tutankhamun - we can witness the dramatic scenes of its discovery and marvel at its extraordinary treasures exactly as they were then, in colour.","genre_ids":[99,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/vWC7yGnBLcIFw7k8EjKEWAFtXgf.jpg","release_date":"2020-06-18","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/ugmFasiQKy4Z7usA3vocLVIbIO6.jpg","original_title":"Tutankhamun In Colour","original_language":"en"},{"id":693400,"adult":false,"title":"Necromantic","video":false,"overview":"A novice teenage witch attempts to woo the love of her life with a love potion, but when things spiral out of control, more twisted measures are taken to win her heart.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5944,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/rlV4bRZk7o6aU7Dl4QrWm9wsiyK.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-14","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Necromantic","original_language":"en"},{"id":422534,"adult":false,"title":"Parallel Lines Meet at Infinity","video":false,"overview":"Sasha is stalking a man. They seem to have a common past, which Sasha can't let go. This leads her into dark territory. For he is an uncompromising photographer, who is obsessively trying to get an exhibition in a gallery. His theme is fear - and to capture this in its perfection, he puts women into shock situations in his photo shoots. In the process, reality and production become blurred, and the models pay the price. One day he turns up at Sasha's door - A dark cocktail of passion and obsession, portraying the borderline facets of photography.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1157,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/69PcTwmXO3wc6JcjK58OrSlCdNj.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-21","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/vJTjPFXbIVwkrQ2NGYsluoF6Ko1.jpg","original_title":"Параллельные прямые пересекаются в бесконечности","original_language":"ru"}],"similar_content":[{"id":763841,"adult":false,"title":"The Love Affair of the Spring and Four Months","video":false,"overview":"An unknown author of Chunhyangjeon and called “Yagokbisa”. Writer Chun Sa-Wol, who has become a hot topic in Jang-an by writing a love story. Falls in love with Baekga, a mysterious man who insists on free dating. One day, the female exorcist Dalgi and the Amhaengeo teacher Inan. They come to the spring and summer months for the purpose of not knowing the reason, Noh Daegam devises a scheme to control the body and mind of Chun-Sa-Wol.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.0836,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/bdHib41KmCnLJUVEREqRdFoOFZC.jpg","release_date":"2020-09-25","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":"/pPA8YbztWiH7h8Lgd7GUCWR8cs6.jpg","original_title":"춘사월의 정사","original_language":"ko"},{"id":947928,"adult":false,"title":"Mistress","video":false,"overview":"Nikkatsu Roman Porno","genre_ids":[10749,53],"popularity":0.17,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/hVNPexTTfQm4b49CVUSdFgW8hQ2.jpg","release_date":"1972-08-26","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"情婦","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1124990,"adult":false,"title":"Red Sister","video":false,"overview":"So Jeong came to Korea to study with the condition that she lives with her relative older brothers. She followed her mother and immigrated to the Philippines when she was young, but she's planning to stay in Korea now that she's given this opportunity. It's a bit unfortunate that relatives' house is not in Seoul, but she decided to endure until graduation. Min Woo and Sang Woo are surprised by So Jeong's appearance they see for the first time since she became an adult. Min Woo is embarrassed by So Jeong, who remembers touching her breasts when she was young. Sang Woo peeps at So Jeong while she's in a shower, and So Jeong begins to be attracted to the opposite sex.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.9075,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/xRTfIPHP1G1PEq0HYY414yKezKX.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-01","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"볼빨간 여동생","original_language":"ko"},{"id":763633,"adult":false,"title":"My Sister, Sister, Sister...","video":false,"overview":"I was once a novelist who was looking forward to the future, but now I am living in a house that is just a handful. I have to write, but the enthusiasm for writing has long been lost. One day when I was bored every day, my friend (Jane) of Sukjep (exponent) comes home. Jane pulls the hair out of her face with a sweaty face on a hot summer day and sits on the front door. When I saw Jane who seemed innocent and innocent and sexy, my heart was rocked ...","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":1.904,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/ebq7uYRnmYqtrOjGdrfJDkyJewG.jpg","release_date":"2019-01-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"처제는, 처제와, 처제의...","original_language":"ko"},{"id":250015,"adult":false,"title":"Hidden Treasures","video":false,"overview":"A beautiful woman brings together a group of her friends in order to search for any treasures that may be hidden throughout a mansion given to her by her deceased father, and the girls find that they are more interested in exploring one another.","genre_ids":[18,10770],"popularity":0.3723,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/g6ki5AvEk2TFu3aCNiRjDkzo7Dw.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-03","vote_average":3.75,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hidden Treasures","original_language":"en"},{"id":251672,"adult":false,"title":"Behind Bedroom Doors","video":false,"overview":"New-girl-in-town Abby is already dating two guys--one's a doctor, the other is running for district attorney. She also has some dirt on both of them---but when they find that she may potentially blackmail them, Abby discovers just how important a career is to some people.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.3182,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/zyUx8K70YCwXF2FE7BHvsnkGU6H.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-16","vote_average":3.857,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Behind Bedroom Doors","original_language":"en"},{"id":249397,"adult":false,"title":"Nymphomaniac: Vol. II","video":false,"overview":"The continuation of Joe's sexually dictated life delves into the darker aspects of her adult life and what led to her being in Seligman's care.","genre_ids":[18,9648],"popularity":9.3136,"vote_count":3085,"poster_path":"/iLUNqgNKuWn667kXCKztSxY