eon Joo...","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.0484,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/qhPS9o8wkmVIC0NVp9uLW8K2VT4.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-12","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/eJEnsni5p2aS5toQJK7w6iOfnsI.jpg","original_title":"아이돌 연습생: 내 여동생의 친구들","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1125423,"adult":false,"title":"어린 여동생 2","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3275,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/qcGDrSUOrXoe4EpdJB10UbD9fbT.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-03","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":"/P6biuFhEFf19lM6zdsYH9d25PE.jpg","original_title":"어린 여동생 2","original_language":"ko"},{"id":419329,"adult":false,"title":"Descendants of Adultery","video":false,"overview":"Soo-ji is a skin specialist who experiences retaliatory driving on her way to work and Captain Kwon helps her. Later, they meet at the hospital and start to feel attracted to each other. Soo-ji is tired of living a pretentious marriage life with her cheating husband and falls in love with Kwon...","genre_ids":[10749],"popularity":1.8763,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/5hDIHNft2A7tlNsFuTKhIJfKKdc.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-30","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/wyDAIoOxdT3lYXtpiJaS1GcjTtX.jpg","original_title":"불륜의 후예","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1472610,"adult":false,"title":"Obscene Trap","video":false,"overview":"Mi-yeon, an elite woman with a mysterious past, and her husband, Yeong-jeon, a novelist who doesn't know her secret. Mi-yeon is the head of a large corporation. She is a woman who enjoys a free-spirited sex life and is married to a novelist, Yeong-jeon. On the other hand, a married couple, Taeh-yeon and Seo-ra, moved into their neighboring house.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.9035,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/cbYshiMJmFNDIWLvt4w9dj95US0.jpg","release_date":"2023-09-22","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"음란의 덫","original_language":"ko"},{"id":16802,"adult":false,"title":"Forbidden","video":false,"overview":"At his bachelor party, Jason has a one-night fling with Nikki, a radiant beauty with whom he forms an immediate bond. They agree to keep their secret locked away forever. Two years later, Jason, his wife, Andy and his fiancee plan a reunion weekend. Jason is shocked to discover that Andy's fiancee is Nikki. Now, secret and passionate affairs are played out.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":6.582,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/kShQ7hGJHk7pJYgWnO7SzkXQ7IY.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-25","vote_average":4.75,"backdrop_path":"/iA24ZK5vyv5weZMTjTyVpGcyrxe.jpg","original_title":"Forbidden","original_language":"en"},{"id":779462,"adult":false,"title":"How to Ruin Housewarming Party","video":false,"overview":"Chae-young was invited to the housewarming party, meets her ex Jeong-yoon, who broke up a year ago. She tries to be cool, but it doesn't clear the air of awkwardness. It even gets worse by Jeong-yoon's new girlfriend joins the party. Chae-young seems so weird with Jeong-yoon's girlfriend and subtle atmosphere inside house... Who do you think ruined this housewarming party?","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.1146,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/pz8kAHKrwZK8qD5EGRHTfstYYjM.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-22","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/4XSqQWLzdk5cwCZWAtknKheHIe0.jpg","original_title":"즐거운 집들이","original_language":"ko"},{"id":605231,"adult":false,"title":"Addicted to Love","video":false,"overview":"A sweet, romantic comedy involving four gay guys in Tokyo. Tadashi is a confused gay Japanese teenager at an all-boys school who fantasizes about his best friend, Kota. Hiroki and Shiji are a young, gay couple living in Tokyo. When Tadashi sees the couple being openly affectionate on the train one day, he decides to follow them. From this strange beginning, the guys decide to help Tadashi deal with the stress of coming out.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":0.2489,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/glbExGOe0XoLHzTpFA1OFf3a5tX.jpg","release_date":"1999-07-31","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"僕は恋に夢中","original_language":"ja"},{"id":605233,"adult":false,"title":"Maybe It's Sad","video":false,"overview":"After graduating from university, Satoshi Takagi joined the advertising agency he had always dreamed of, and started his working life with great enthusiasm. Satoshi has a boyfriend who is more than a friend but less than a lover, but even when she tries to talk to him about the company, he only wants Satoshi's body and won't listen at all. “Am I just a body?” The distance between him and Satoshi has widened a little. Despite this, Satoshi did his best at work. He was actually starting to be attracted to his boss, Furukawa. However, Furukawa is a straight man who is dating Satoshi's colleague, an office lady. Although it is a dream that cannot come true after all, my feelings for Furukawa, who does his job in a cool manner, grows stronger every day.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2976,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/nRDl1RbJZa9N2VmNkVzVy1NThHv.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-17","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"せつないかもしれない","original_language":"ja"},{"id":779677,"adult":false,"title":"Banned: Woman's Secret Pictures","video":false,"overview":"A man spies on an upper class woman having an illicit affair and blackmails her for sex. But she’s not the delicate flower that she appears to be.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3258,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/wo8sXpAwI6npGMslDtBcYElckeq.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-02","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":"/A37WqjwfoztYz1dgjhFlc7ic959.jpg","original_title":"発禁　秘画のおんな","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15794,"adult":false,"title":"White Heat","video":false,"overview":"A psychopathic criminal with a mother complex makes a daring break from prison and then leads his old gang in a chemical plant payroll heist. After the heist, events take a crazy turn.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":1.7716,"vote_count":525,"poster_path":"/v7cPOHKKZI9qChi7HDUxNIhEcLR.jpg","release_date":"1949-09-02","vote_average":7.655,"backdrop_path":"/cap8458wFeRCJSKxL758dI82TRK.jpg","original_title":"White Heat","original_language":"en"},{"id":15802,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo Decadence","video":false,"overview":"A submissive hooker goes about her trade, suffering abuse at the hands of Japanese salarymen and Yakuza types. She's unhappy about her work, and is apparently trying to find some sort of appeasement for the fact that her lover has married.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.7996,"vote_count":119,"poster_path":"/ya3HsnwavmtQYMxnGS5T5RV6do0.jpg","release_date":"1992-01-06","vote_average":5.933,"backdrop_path":"/yetPav6Lpo30pl8RE5jaXFCgsIa.jpg","original_title":"トパーズ","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt5306218","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":104063,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"JP","release_dates":[{"note":"R15 version, OP PICTURES+ Fest 2016","type":2,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2016-08-21T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"R15+"},{"note":"R18 version","type":2,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2015-12-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"R18+"},{"note":"DVD OPPS-001","type":5,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2017-10-04T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"R15+"}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"original_network":null,"screenwriters":null,"based_on":null,"filming_location":null,"narrative_location":null,"review_score_rt":null,"review_score_mc":null,"box_office":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"collection_id":null,"wikidata_metadata":{},"mood_tags":null,"trope_tags":null,"vibe_description":null,"ai_enriched_at":null,"ai_enrichment_version":0}}]]
9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/104063/the-secret-game-of-the-immoral-wife"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/104063/the-secret-game-of-the-immoral-wife"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/euDNoIcpeW69gJBUYktR0hewq47.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Secret Game of the Immoral Wife"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"From the first moment, Haruo saw Makoto in a busy street crossing, it was love at first sight. He spent five years stalking her and looking at her in her house through binoculars from his apartment across the street. Watching Makoto’s seemingly perfect life with her husband became a daily habit for him. He even mastered lip-reading in order to act out conversations with her. One day. Haruo witnesses Makoto’s husband, Mikiya, having sex with another woman. To expose her cheating husband’s lies, Haruo takes photos of the incident and sends them to Makoto, along with a letter, However, when she receives the photos, she throws them away without any reaction, and their normal husband-and-wife routine resumes as if nothing happened. [Exists in 2 versions: the original R18 version, and the R15 edit version]"}],"$L12","$L13","$L14"],"error":null,"digest":"$undefined"}
